{"article_id":"dzRoEtVcLmlEG5qH","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"LISTEN TO ARTICLE 4:55","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"SHARE THIS ARTICLE","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"Share Tweet","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"Post Email","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"Donald Trump welcomed home three Americans","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"released from detention in North Korea in the dark of Thursday morning ,","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"thanking that country ' s leader Kim Jong Un","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"and reiterating","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"that his goal in an upcoming summit is to rid the Korean peninsula of nuclear weapons .","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"The three men flew to Washington after their release to Secretary of State Mike Pompeo ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"who was dispatched to Pyongyang on Tuesday in the hope","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"that Kim would agree to free the detainees .","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"Trump and his wife Melania boarded the former prisoners ' plane at Joint Base Andrews shortly before 3 a.m. on Thursday","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"to greet the men .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"\" It ' s like a dream .","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"And we are very , very happy , \"","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"one of the released detainees , Kim Dong Chul , said through a translator","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"when asked how it felt to be home ,","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"according to a transcript","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"released by the White House .","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"Asked how they were treated by the North Koreans ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"he said ,","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"\" We were treated in many different ways .","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"For me , I had to do a lot of labor .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"But","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"when I got sick ,","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"I was also treated by them . \"","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"The return of prisoners","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"the U.S. has called \" hostages \"","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"clears an obstacle to direct talks between Trump and Kim .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"The president said on Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"that he expects to announce a date and location for the summit within days","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"and that he had ruled out the Korea Peninsula ' s Demilitarized Zone .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"An administration official later said","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"that he is leaning toward Singapore .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Trump thanked Kim","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"for releasing the men .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"\" This is a special night for these three really great people","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"and congratulations","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"on being in this country , \"","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"Trump told reporters at the airbase .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"\" The fact","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"that we were able to get them out so soon","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"was really a tribute to a lot of things ,","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"including a certain process","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"that ' s taking place right now .","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"And that process is very important . \"","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"The U.S. aims to persuade Kim to give up his country ' s nuclear arsenal ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"and Trump has engaged in what he calls a \" maximum pressure \" campaign","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"to ratchet up sanctions on North Korea","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"and lean on other nations","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"to cut diplomatic ties .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"Read more :","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"Why Trump and Kim May Pick Singapore for Their Summit","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"\" I really think","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"we have a very good chance","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"of doing something very meaningful , \"","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"\" I really think","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"he wants to do something","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"and bring that country into the real world , \"","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"he said of Kim .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Trump with Kim Sang Dok ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"also known as Tony Kim , second right ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"and Kim Dong Chul , second right .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"Photographer :","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Andrew Harrer/","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"\" The true honor is going to be","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"if we have a victory","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"in getting rid of nuclear weapons , \"","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Senator Angus King of Maine , an independent","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"who caucuses with Democrats ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"warned against taking a victory lap","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"until a deal is in place .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"\" A word of caution :","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"We ' re not there yet , \"","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"King said on CNN .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"The former detainees are all Korean-American men","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"who share the common surname Kim","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"but are not related .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"They were handed over to Pompeo during his second trip to Pyongyang this year , a visit","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"that wasn ' t announced","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"before Trump himself disclosed it on Tuesday","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"while the secretary of state was in the air .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Asked if he might visit Pyongyang himself in the future ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Trump said","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"it \" could happen. \"","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"He joked","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"that the homecoming event would set a \" 3 a.m. \" television ratings record .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"\" We would like to express our deep appreciation to the United States government , President Trump , Secretary Pompeo , and the people of the United States","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"for bringing us home , \"","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"the detainees said in a statement","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"as they flew to Washington .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"\" We thank God , and all our families and friends","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"who prayed for us and for our return .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"God Bless America , the greatest nation in the world . \"","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Kim Dong Chul was sentenced to 10 years hard labor in 2016 on charges","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"he conducted espionage for South Korea .","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"South Korea ' s intelligence agency denied any ties to the man .","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"Kim Hak Song was detained last year for what North Korean media described as \" hostile acts \" against the country .","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"Kim Sang Dok ,","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"also known as Tony Kim ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"was intercepted in April 2017 at Pyongyang International Airport","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"after being invited to teach accounting at Pyongyang University of Science and Technology .","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"The homecoming event was broadcast live on cable news networks ,","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"and the men were greeted by a large American flag","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"strung between two fire trucks","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"parked on the tarmac .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Pompeo was informed after a meeting with Kim Jong Un on Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"that the men had been granted \" amnesty. \"","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"They were brought to the airport","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"and left North Korea on Pompeo ' s plane at about 8:42 p.m. local time on Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"The secretary of state and the detainees arrived at Joint Base Andrews on Thursday on separate planes .","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"Trump with First Lady Melania Trump at the White House","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"following an event at Joint Base Andrews on May 10 .","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"Photographer :","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"Yuri Gripas/","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence ,","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"who joined Trump at the homecoming ,","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"said Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"that all three men \" seem to be in good health \"","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"and were glad to be heading home .","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"Pence also spoke Wednesday with the parents of Otto Warmbier , the American college student","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"who had been detained in North Korea","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"for trying to steal a propaganda poster from a hotel .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Warmbier died","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"shortly after being returned home from North Korea in a coma last year .","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"After meeting Trump and Pence","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"the former detainees boarded a bus","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"to travel to Walter Reed military hospital in Bethesda , Maryland for evaluation and any treatment .","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"Pence , meanwhile , said on Twitter","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"he would sit for interviews with NBC , ABC and CBS","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"to be broadcast on their morning news programs .","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"`` Promises were made","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"and then promises were broken .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"But the promises weren ' t made by North Korea","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"until there were concessions , ''","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"Pence said during an interview with CBS News .","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"Kim ' s agreement","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"to release the three","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"`` Gives us hope","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"that this may be different . ''","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"- With assistance by Nick Wadhams , David Tweed , Jennifer Epstein , and Terrence Dopp","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":287,"left":0,"right":286,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":286,"left":247,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":220,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":196,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":194,"right":195,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":169,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":146,"right":168,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":1,"right":145,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":168,"left":153,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":150,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":147,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":6,"right":148,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":152,"left":9,"right":151,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":154,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":159,"right":165,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":157,"right":158,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":155,"right":156,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":14,"right":15